      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1b64750c-f3ba-80ec-bd1f-d828db243778",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The similarity between pre-requisites and course metadata are the mechanism used to determine the recommendations. Results of experimental tests reveal promising Accuracy scores.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b64750c-f3ba-80ec-bd1f-d828db243778",
